<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="x-ua-compatible" content="ie=edge" />
    <title>Invitation</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>Hey there, {{usermail}},</p>
    
    <p>
      I'm barking up your inbox to extend a paw-some invitation: Join our team workspace on 
      fetchrocket! 🐾🚀 We're wagging our tails with excitement to have you onboard as we 
      collaborate on essential organization info powered by AI.
    </p>

    <p>
      By joining our workspace, you'll unlock a whole world of tail-wagging perks, including:
    </p>

    <p>📁 Access to shared files</p>
    <p>💡 Instant answers to questions on shared info</p>
    <p>🤖 Interactions with multiple AI assistants</p>

    <p>
      Ready to dive in? Just click on the link below to join our fetchrocket pack: 
    </p>

    <p>
      <a 
        href={{acceptLink}} 
        style="background-color: rgb(22, 207, 93); color: #fff; padding: 5px; border-radius: 2px; margin-right: 20px; text-decoration: none"
      >
        Accept Invitation
      </a>

      <a 
        href={{denyLink}} 
        style="background-color: rgb(154, 13, 13); color: #fff; padding: 5px; border-radius: 2px; text-decoration: none">
          Deny
      </a>
    </p>

    <p>
      Once you're in, you'll have access to all the shared files, projects, and communication 
      channels – it's like having a secret clubhouse just for us!
    </p>

    <p>
      If you need any help getting started or have questions along the way, don't hesitate to 
      reach out to me or [admin's name and email]. We're here to lend a helping paw whenever 
      you need it.
    </p>

    <p>
      We're wagging our tails in anticipation of having you collaborate with us on fetchrocket!
    </p>
    <p>Best woofs and tail wags,</p>
    <p>{{sender}}</p>
  </body>
</html>
